# Holocron - Exclude plaintext markdown files from Git
# Only encrypted .md.enc files should be committed

# Exclude all plaintext .md files in the notes directory
notes/**/*.md

# Include encrypted files
!notes/**/*.md.enc

# Include encrypted config (safe to commit - encrypted with machine key)
!.holocron/config.json.enc

# Exclude other local files
.holocron/*
!.holocron/config.json.enc
